snippet.textDisplay: Dear Sachin and Jiagar, I have no word to say...my eyes have a tear of that feelings. Basically I am work in one Special Care Home for orphan girls. And as like Tanu with me 47 girls are attached. So, my each second with my daughters reflected in this song. It is lovely...Just like Sugar. Without eating no once can realize the test...Music is totally amazing. Fabulous. Kirti Danji and Rekhaji .... OMG ...they are magician of sur tal and lay...Great great great work. I like the line much more 'Fari Zali le maro hath..' In last week when I got this song first time, every day I listen more than 40-50 times. And each time my eye have a carton of tear...I love it. Abhinandan to all team.
